#: ../../configuration/protocols/bgp.rst:113
msgid "**Router-ID check**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../configuration/protocols/bgp.rst:115
msgid ""
"Prefer the route with the lowest `router-ID`. If the route has an "
"`ORIGINATOR_ID` attribute, through iBGP reflection, then that router ID "
"is used, otherwise the `router-ID` of the peer the route was received "
"from is used."
