" are several open source implementations to choose from, such as "
"NLNetLabs' Routinator_ (written in Rust), Cloudflare's GoRTR_ and "
"OctoRPKI_ (written in Go), and RIPE NCC's RPKI Validator_ (written in "
"Java). The RTR protocol is described in :rfc:`8210`."
