"source address, destination address, layer-4 protocol, layer-4 key) "
"tuple. The layer-4 key depends on the transport protocol; for TCP/UDP it "
"is the port numbers, for tunnels it can be their tunnel ID, but otherwise"
" is just zero, as if it were not part of the tuple. To be able to inspect"
" the TCP port in all cases, packets will be mandatorily defragmented."
